    • Method Detail

      • createThumbnail

        public static Image createThumbnail(InputStream is,
                    String name,
                    Dimension scaledSize,
                    String mimeType)
        This method takes a input document (represented by an InputStream) and returns a byte[] representing a JPEG "thumb nail" of a given page of the document. It can do this for a limited number of input document "types"images.
        Parameters:
        is - The InputStream representing the input document.
        name - The name of the file from which the input document was sourced.
        scaledSize - the size to which the given image is to be scaled, null for default
        mimeType - the mime type
        Returns:
        a byte[] array representing a JEPG thumb nail of the specified page within the Office document or Image.
